{"tid":783531,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)dead rising 活死人地帶 活死人凶間","createTime":"2018-08-17T15:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T19:17:06.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"44442ec3672bcf1141658e0ae9bff8f44965bb97","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b8028e04\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2e3dc39d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4306d800\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hd.club.tw/data/attachment/forum/201502/16/152625u4zuni488uwurwz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hd.club.tw%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201502%2F16%2F152625u4zuni488uwurwz5.jpg&h=380985f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-pKPx5vs6RnU/V3i0lh4RI7I/AAAAAAAAHtU/dxVcmwmLrPgGSYIJ6IgFmjOeeLlFRY0jwCLcB/s1600/dead+rising1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-pKPx5vs6RnU%2FV3i0lh4RI7I%2FAAAAAAAAHtU%2FdxVcmwmLrPgGSYIJ6IgFmjOeeLlFRY0jwCLcB%2Fs1600%2Fdead%2Brising1.jpg&h=5fdaf078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/a/a6/Dawn_Of_The_Dead.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fa%2Fa6%2FDawn_Of_The_Dead.jpg&h=df38f70c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://5.blog.xuite.net/5/8/2/f/12092670/blog_141852/txt/9049154/8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5.blog.xuite.net%2F5%2F8%2F2%2Ff%2F12092670%2Fblog_141852%2Ftxt%2F9049154%2F8.jpg&h=e3c7a38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事設定在 Dead Rising 2 及Dead Rising 3之間，記者Chase (Jess Metcalfe 飾)跟女攝影師 Jordan Blair 在 East Mission的隔離區採訪有關 Zombrex 疫苗專題，誰知疫苗未能發揮作用，再引發另一場喪屍潮。在逃亡路上，Chase 遇上Zombrex 用家Crystal及尋找女兒的媽媽 Maggie，四人一方面要防止被咬，一方面尋找爆發原因，最終發現一切是政府的陰謀所致...<br />\n<br />\n2.一名居住在美國威斯康辛州密爾瓦基（Milwaukee）名叫安娜（Ana）的護士，在一如往常回到家休息。但隔天她的生活完全變了，丈夫變成了喪屍。好不容易開車逃離住宅，才知道整座城市已經陷入混亂，但突然有人要搶奪安娜的汽車，而撞上了一棵樹，安娜就暫時昏迷。（此時片頭音樂&quot;The Man Comes Around&quot;播放中，音樂還夾雜著各地因喪屍而陷入混亂的畫面）<br />\n<br />\n3.人類創造的文明世界已成為遙遠的記憶，現在的世界是一個無止無盡的噩夢，活人不斷受到活屍的攻擊，被它們生吞活剝，於是碩果僅存的人類為了活下去，只能躲在圍牆高築、防衛嚴密的城市堡壘，竭力抵抗活屍的攻擊。<br />\n少數有錢有勢的特權份子住在市內的綠洲高級大樓社區，在可怕活屍的威脅之下，試圖製造日子照舊的假象，維持著夜夜笙歌的糜爛生活。但是在大樓以外的城市街頭，平民百姓卻過著苦不堪言的生活，他們每天活在死亡的陰影之下，只能藉由賭博和嗑藥來麻醉自己，逃避這種地獄般的生活..<br />\n<br />\n11 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5dd3c308\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=HznOOnqaT1YeGSJD2gOPpS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ebeab9b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f6ed6cc4bf8e7b19941bc2b601e69316c30489","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a59e7860a88c40f28c41086db3a3687606d96f","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c56df0679771f55bfc76c54a58f333476a009c","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cf9d9ee118b43d3715f1ab72ac7845769b2c59","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7fefeb034a1e10e12c2658a920242d15ae5afd","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T18:56:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252c456d2db2492b47f08633ad56c9c479bc67c4","tid":783531,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor